<i>I need you to get everybody
out of the house as quickly as possible.</i>

278
00:38:10,952 --> 00:38:14,251
<i>We'll send a car immediately.
Ma'am, are you alone?</i>

279
00:38:14,322 --> 00:38:15,914
No, I'm with... I'm with...

280
00:38:15,991 --> 00:38:17,049
Ben!

281
00:38:29,304 --> 00:38:30,362
Ben!

282
00:38:47,322 --> 00:38:48,380
Ben?

283
00:38:58,266 --> 00:39:00,166
Ben, what are you...

284
00:39:02,003 --> 00:39:03,095
Ben!

285
