But that he didn't see anything unusual
in the house.

301
00:41:00,221 --> 00:41:04,749
Mom, please believe me.
I'm not making this up. I'm telling the truth.

302
00:41:04,826 --> 00:41:06,293
Jess, please.

303
00:41:07,896 --> 00:41:09,227
Just stop.

304
