-Maybe we're in over our heads here, Roy.
-We'll get through this.

318
00:42:48,296 --> 00:42:50,696
Just give her some time. She'll be fine.

319
00:43:00,542 --> 00:43:02,635
You saw it too, didn't you?

320
00:43:06,681 --> 00:43:09,411
Come on. I know you did. You had to have.

321
00:43:10,385 --> 00:43:12,444
Just tell me.

322
