Hey, you didn't hear that.

331
00:48:23,464 --> 00:48:26,194
-Dad said you needed this.
-Yeah, thanks.

332
00:48:28,202 --> 00:48:32,002
Why did you tell my parents
you didn't see anything last night?

333
00:48:32,673 --> 00:48:34,573
Well, because I didn't.

334
00:48:37,011 --> 00:48:39,707
I mean, look, I know you were scared.

335
00:48:40,581 --> 00:48:46,076
And I know that people,
even your parents, sometimes,

336
00:48:46,153 --> 00:48:49,316
-they don't know how to listen.
-Especially my parents.

337
00:48:49,390 --> 00:48:53,793
They got pressures
that you can't even begin to understand.

338
00:48:57,899 --> 00:49:00,595
You sure you saw something up there?

339
00:49:00,668 --> 00:49:03,865
I saw it. It was real.

340
00:49:05,306 --> 00:49:08,036
Maybe you've just got a lot on your mind.

341
00:49:21,088 --> 00:49:22,919
Hey, Jess.

342
00:49:22,990 --> 00:49:25,220
-Hey. Thanks for coming.
-Yeah.

343
00:49:27,395 --> 00:49:29,829
You don't look so good. Whaùs up?

344
00:49:31,933 --> 00:49:34,424
Did you know the family
