345
00:49:34,502 --> 00:49:36,902
Not really. It was the Rollins that lived there.

346
00:49:36,971 --> 00:49:38,165
What happened to them?

347
00:49:38,239 --> 00:49:41,572
They just up and left
about five, six years ago.

348
00:49:41,642 --> 00:49:45,339
There were some bad harvests.
Lot of people didn't make it.

349
00:49:47,581 --> 00:49:48,741
Hey...

350
00:49:50,384 --> 00:49:55,481
Did you ever hear of anything
about my house being, like, haunted?

351
00:50:00,027 --> 00:50:01,358
Seriously.

352
00:50:01,462 --> 00:50:05,023
Just, like, stupid stories.
Iùs been abandoned for a long time. So...

353
00:50:05,099 --> 00:50:07,727
-What kind of stories?
-Nothing really.

354
