364
00:54:15,749 --> 00:54:18,183
-Get away from what?
-I don't know.

365
00:54:18,852 --> 00:54:20,479
But she was...

366
00:54:20,554 --> 00:54:23,887
She looked just scared to death.

367
00:54:31,065 --> 00:54:32,930
